videos.description: West Virginia guard Miles McBride strips it away then finds Emmitt Matthews Jr. in transition for the massive two-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McBride connects with Matthews for the alley-oop) 2020/12/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: McBride connects with Matthews for the alley-oop

videos.description: After grabbing the offensive rebound, Dante Harris drives down the baseline and quickly feeds it to Timothy Ighoefe for the slam.
